item.title:
Margot Robbie on #Barbie being sexualized:
“People can project sex onto her. Yes, she can wear a short skirt, but because it’s fun and pink. Not because she wanted you to see her butt.”

item.title:
Ryan Gosling reveals that Margot Robbie sent him a gift every day to help him develop his character as Ken:
“She left a pink present with a pink bow, from Barbie to Ken, every day while we were filming. They were all beach-related.”
item.author: PopBase
